## Interface: 120005, 50503, 20505, 11508, 120007
## Title: Cairn-Gui-Demo-2.0
## Notes: Live, browseable showcase of every Cairn-Gui-2.0 feature. /cgdemo opens a tabbed window with one tab per surface (widgets, layouts, themes, primitives, animations, events, L10n, secure widgets, contracts, inspector). Author-facing reference; not required by any other addon.
## Author: ChronicTinkerer
## Version: 1
## Dependencies: Cairn
## X-Category: Development Tools
## X-License: MIT
## DefaultState: enabled
## LoadOnDemand: 0

# Core: init, slash command, root Window + TabGroup shell. Each Tabs/*.lua
# below builds out one tab against the shared shell.
Core.lua

# Code-snippet strings shared across tabs (so each tab file stays focused
# on rendering, not on quoting itself in Lua).
Snippets.lua

# Tabs (load after Core since they call into the registration API on it).
Tabs\Welcome.lua
Tabs\Buttons.lua
Tabs\Inputs.lua
Tabs\Containers.lua
Tabs\Layouts.lua
Tabs\LayoutsExtra.lua
Tabs\Themes.lua
Tabs\Primitives.lua
Tabs\Animations.lua
Tabs\Events.lua
Tabs\L10n.lua
Tabs\Inspector.lua
Tabs\Secure.lua
Tabs\Contracts.lua
